sequenceDiagram

    participant U as Client (Web/App)
    participant G as WS Gateway
    participant S as Session Manager
    participant A as Audio Processor
    participant V as VAD
    participant STT as STT Stream
    participant LLM as LLM Stream
    participant TTS as TTS Stream
    participant Q as Queue Manager
    participant I as Interrupt Ctrl

    %% =====================
    %% Connect
    %% =====================

    U->>G: WebSocket Connect (session_id, token)
    G->>S: create / attach session
    S-->>G: ok
    G-->>U: 101 Switching Protocols

    %% =====================
    %% Audio Input Loop
    %% =====================

    loop audio stream
        U->>G: binary audio chunk
        G->>S: forward audio
        S->>A: decode / resample
        A->>V: audio frame
        V-->>S: speech / silence

        S->>STT: stream audio
        STT-->>S: partial text
        S->>Q: append text buffer
    end

    %% =====================
    %% Silence trigger
    %% =====================

    V-->>S: silence > threshold

    S->>Q: finalize text
    Q-->>S: text

    S->>LLM: send prompt (history + text)

    %% =====================
    %% LLM streaming
    %% =====================

    loop token stream

        LLM-->>S: token delta
        S->>Q: append token

        S->>Q: phrase detect
        Q-->>S: phrase ready

        S->>TTS: send phrase

        TTS-->>S: audio chunk

        S->>Q: push audio

        Q-->>G: audio chunk
        G-->>U: binary audio

    end

    %% =====================
    %% Interrupt
    %% =====================

    U->>G: new audio (user speak)

    G->>S: interrupt

    S->>I: cancel request

    I->>LLM: cancel
    I->>TTS: cancel
    I->>Q: clear audio
    I->>Q: clear token

    I-->>S: done

    S-->>U: stop audio

    %% =====================
    %% Continue conversation
    %% =====================

    loop next turn
        U->>G: audio
    end